metadata.name: Sneakers be happy
metadata.description:
This photo was taken on April 24, 2020 in Bangkok, Thailand. It was crazy COVID period and people were quite scared of the close talking. This Thai girl was probably a student. Perhaps even the sneaker has the best thoughts it can convey to the world. When you purchase this NFT, you will also get access and rights to the original video story of this stranger and the sneaker
